                <h1>iPhone Wallpaper Settings: Customize Your Screen</h1>
                <p>To change your wallpaper settings on iPhone, go to Settings > Wallpaper. Here, you can select "Choose a New Wallpaper" to browse your photo library or Apple's stock images. Adjust the wallpaper for your lock screen, home screen, or both. Don't forget to preview how it looks before setting it!</p>
